    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if there isn't a solution? what if the \"pain in the long run\" is just the nature of things? it feels like people only say that because they're afraid of the alternative. it's hard to believe in a \"fix\" when everything feels so permanent and heavy. it just feels like a loop of suffering over and over.",
